            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-Hd1e108">Rubrica 21</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De decimarum et primitiarum religione</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>¶ De decimarum et primi
      <lb ed="#V" n="18" break="no"/>tiarum religione. Rubrica. 21.
      
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>I exodo. 2 <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-Qd1e125">heia
        <lb ed="#V" n="20" break="no"/>mas tuas et
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>primitias non tardabis offerre. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-d1e133">
               <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>
               / <ref>23. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-Qd1e137">Primitias frugum terre tue
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>deferre in domu domini dei tui. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-d1e144"> /
               <ref>25. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-Qd1e146">Loquire
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>filiis istlis: vt tollat mihi pramitias ab omni homine
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>qui offert vltro ne accipies eas </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-d1e154">
               <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-Qd1e158">¶ In leuitico. c. vlt. Omnes decime terre siue de
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>frugibus siue de pomis arborum domino sunt:
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>et illi sanctificantur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-d1e166"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-Qd1e168"> Boues et oues et ca
        <lb ed="#V" n="29" break="no"/>pre que pastoris virga transeunt quicquid
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>decimum venerit sanctificabitur domino. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-d1e176">
               <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>
               ¶<ref>In libro numeri. ca. 18.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-Qd1e180">Locutus est dominus
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>ad aaron etc. filiis leui dedi omnes decimas
        <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>israelis in possessionem pro ministerio quo set
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>uiunt mihi in tabernaculo federis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-d1e190"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-Qd1e192"> Nihil
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>aliud possidebunt filii leui decimarum oblatio
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>ne contenti: quis in vsus eorum et necessariis sepaui </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-d1e200">
               <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>
               ¶ <ref>Moyses in deuteronomio. c. 14.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-Qd1e204">Deciman
        <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>partem separabis de cunctis fructibus tuis qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>nascuntur in terra per annos singulos: et co
        <lb ed="#V" n="40" break="no"/>medes in conspectu domini dei tui in loco quem
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>elegerit: vt in eo nomen illius inuocetur: deci
        <lb ed="#V" n="42" break="no"/>ma frumenti tui et vini et olei: et primogenita de
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>armentis et ouibus tnis: vt discas timere dominum
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>deum tuum omnitepore. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-d1e224"> /
               <ref>c. 18.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-Qd1e226">Non habebunt sacer
        <lb ed="#V" n="45" break="no"/>dotes et leuite: et omnes qui de eadem tribu sunt <!--38.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>partem et heditatem cum reliquo pistolo istuis: quia sa
        <lb ed="#V" n="47" break="no"/>crificia domini et oblationes eius comedent: et nihil
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>aliud accipiant de portione fratrum suorum: dominus
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>enim ipse est hbeditas eorum sicut locutus est illis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-d1e245">
               <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>
               ¶ <ref>Salomodo in prouer. c. 3.</ref>  <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de5998-Qd1e249">Honora dominum de tua
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>substantia: et de primitiis omnium frugum tuarum: et
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>implebuntur horrea tua saturitate: et vino tor
        <lb ed="#V" n="53" break="no"/>cularia tua redundabunt </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
